00:24:25,380 --> 00:24:26,495
Ya.

412
00:24:39,160 --> 00:24:40,705
Halo, ini Seung Soo.

413
00:24:41,301 --> 00:24:43,675
Bisakah Departemen Pencari Bakat datang ke kantorku?

414
00:24:43,831 --> 00:24:45,546
"Pelempar Dreams Yoo Min Ho"

415
00:24:45,600 --> 00:24:48,316
"Pemukul Viking Lee Chang Kwon"

416
00:24:58,051 --> 00:25:00,455
Kamu pulang dengan selamat semalam?

417
00:25:00,581 --> 00:25:01,796
Ya.

418
00:25:02,120 --> 00:25:04,450
Tim terburuk tahun ini berhak memilih pertama

419
00:25:04,450 --> 00:25:06,995
